  "description": "This individual is a human ship-captain of middle years, marked by a bronze skinTone set against steady gray eyes. Black hair is kept in a plain, close-managed style that emphasizes a broad forehead and a square, weather-worn jaw. The hands show permanent thickening at the knuckles and palms consistent with long command at sea, and a slight break-set bend at the nose fixes an uncompromising profile. Their carriage is upright and directive, reflecting a life spent issuing orders under pressure.",
